## ⚙️ Installation
```bash
# Backend
Flask
FastAPI
cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt
python main.py

# Frontend
cd frontend
npm install
npm start
        
🛠️ Installation & Setup Instructions
Backend
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/SmartFishNet.git
cd SmartFishNet/backend

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

